# Zookeeper C++ client library

## Requirements

- cmake
- boost
- log4cxx
- cppunit

# How to Build

1) Create a build directory and run cmake followed by make.

    $ mkdir build
    $ cmake ..
    $ make

2) To run all the unit tests, do:

    $ ./zktest

   You can run an individual test suite. For example, to run TestCppClient, do:

    $ ./zktest TestCppClient

   You can also specify an individual test case like this:

    $ ./zktest TestCppClient::testCreate

